              <div class="product-features">
                <span class="feature">Pureza: 98%+</span>
                <span class="feature">Máxima capacidad</span>
                <span class="feature">Certificación internacional</span>
              </div>
              <div class="product-actions">
                <a href="https://wa.me/51952810107?text=Hola%2C%20me%20interesa%20cotizar%20Cianuro%20de%20Sodio%20Cajas%201100kg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Solicitar Cotización</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-image">
              <Image src={sodaCaustica} width={500} height={250} alt="Soda Cáustica" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>Soda Cáustica</h3>
              <p>Soda cáustica de alta pureza, disponible en presentaciones de escamas o perlas, ideal para aplicaciones industriales exigentes.</p>
              <div class="product-features">
                <span class="feature">Pureza: 99%+</span>
                <span class="feature">Múltiples aplicaciones</span>
                <span class="feature">Grado alimentario</span>
              </div>
              <div class="product-actions">
                <a href="https://wa.me/51952810107?text=Hola%2C%20me%20interesa%20cotizar%20Soda%20Cáustica" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Solicitar Cotización</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="certifications-section">
          <h2>Especialistas en Productos Mineros</h2>
          <div class="certifications-grid">
            <div class="cert-card">
              <div class="cert-icon">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M3 21h18l-9-18-9 18zM12 9v4m0 4h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Soluciones para Minería</h4>
              <p>Insumos mineros clave como cianuro de sodio para procesos de lixiviación.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card">
              <div class="cert-icon">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M21 12c.552 0 1-.448 1-1V5c0-.552-.448-1-1-1H3c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v6c0 .552.448 1 1 1h9l4-4 4 4h1z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Productos de Alta Pureza</h4>
              <p>Productos con estándares certificados para uso industrial.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card">
              <div class="cert-icon">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <path d="M16 8l-6 6-2-2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Seguridad y Logística Garantizada</h4>
              <p>Transporte y almacenamiento bajo protocolos estrictos y normativa vigente.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonials-section">
          <h2>Solicitar Cotización</h2>
          <div class="contact-options">
            <a href="https://wa.me/51952810107?text=Hola%2C%20me%20interesa%20solicitar%20una%20cotización%20de%20productos%20mineros" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-card whatsapp-card">
              <div class="contact-icon">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.890-5.335 11.893-11.893A11.821 11.821 0 0020.51 3.488"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>WhatsApp</h4>
                <p>Contáctanos directamente</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="mailto:mfalconi@imexse.com,pfalconi@imexse.com?subject=Solicitud%20de%20Cotización%20-%20Productos%20Mineros&body=Estimados%20señores%2C%0A%0AMe%20dirijo%20a%20ustedes%20para%20solicitar%20una%20cotización%20de%20productos%20mineros.%0A%0AEstaré%20atento%20a%20su%20respuesta.%0A%0ASaludos%20cordiales." class="contact-card email-card">
              <div class="contact-icon">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
                  <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>Correo Electrónico</h4>
                <p>Envíanos tu consulta</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppFloat />
</Layout>

<style>
  .productos {
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #0891b2 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    color: white;
  }

  .products-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(500px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .product-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .product-image {
    height: 250px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .product-info {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .product-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .product-info p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .product-features {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .feature {
    background: #f3f4f6;
    color: #1e40af;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .product-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ea580c 0%, #dc2626 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: white;
  }

  .certifications-section {
    background: #f8fafc;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .certifications-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .certifications-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .cert-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .cert-icon {
    color: #ea580c;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cert-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .cert-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .testimonials-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .contact-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .whatsapp-card {
    border-color: #25d366;
  }

  .whatsapp-card:hover {
    border-color: #25d366;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25d366 0%, #128c7e 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .email-card {
    border-color: #1e40af;
  }

  .email-card:hover {
    border-color: #1e40af;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .whatsapp-card .contact-icon {
    background: #25d366;
    color: white;
  }

  .email-card .contact-icon {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-info h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-card:hover .contact-info p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .productos {
      margin-top: 70px;
    }

    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .products-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .product-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .certifications-section h2,
    .testimonials-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
